These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, eggplant, artichoke
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, videographer, fisherman
1. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
2. the writer is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
3. the writer is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
5. the videographer is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | artichoke | spinach | eggplant |
| Job    | videographer    | fisherman | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, video-games, gardening
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, subway, scooter
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | video-games | gardening | chess |
| Transport   | scooter    | subway     | car        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling, drawing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, trance, gospel
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | drawing     | traveling | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | trance | rock     | gospel  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, animation, family
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | animation  | mystery  |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | rugby | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, collecting, dancing
There are 3 different nationalities: american, polish, spanish
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the american##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
3. the spanish is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | fishing   | dancing | collecting    |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish     | american |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, dancing, singing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, snowboarding, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | dancing | singing | chess   |
| Sport   | cycling     | swimming    | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel, western
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, goldfish
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | fantasy | time-travel |
| Pet           | hamster         | chinchilla         | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, nectarine, grapes
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, dog
1. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the pony and the person eating avocado##2
2. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | nectarine | grapes | avocado |
| Pet    | pony    | bird | dog     |

