.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, soul, metal
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | soul  | gospel  |
| Sport         | soccer | surfing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, lemonade, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: onion, cauliflower, lime
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person eating lime is in an even position##4
3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | iced-tea      | lemonade |
| Food       | cauliflower | lime | onion   |

