.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, paramedic, entrepreneur
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, bike
1. the entrepreneur is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person driving the airplane is the scientist##1
3. the person driving the bike is the entrepreneur##1
4. the entrepreneur is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | paramedic | entrepreneur | scientist |
| Transport   | skateboard | bike   | airplane |

