The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the egyptian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | canadian | brazilian | egyptian |
| Transport     | snowmobile     | ship   | quad-bike        |

