.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, traveling, drawing
3 different pets are kept: bird, rat, turtle
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the owner of the rat##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | traveling | drawing | board-games |
| Pet     | bird    | turtle  | rat   |

