.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, scientific, crime
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, house, trance
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
4. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | crime     | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | house | dubstep | trance    |

